channel.title: Codefasga server status?
channel.description: My server is running i know that for a fact because it posted on moparscape and people are currently playing on it. But whenever i go to post it on codefasga.com it says an unknown error has occured. At first i thought it might be because my old server HAD been on their. But its not anymore and that port is completely closed. Any ideas on how to fix this problem?
